Trump: Lokacin taron West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara kamfen dinsa na farko a wannan yammacin a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, wanda ya hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
An dage zaben da ya tabbatar da zabensa na cike gurbin da ke kan Kotun Koli, kuma Trump na kokarin gina goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke gab da rasa iko a kan majalisa, yayin da za a kirga kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a garin Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yamma, ET yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar YouTube live a kasa.
Trump na iya yin jawabi game da sauraron da aka yi a wannan makon na mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama abin tashin hankali game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da kawo jinkirin yanke hukuncin amincewa da majalisar dattawa na mako guda kafin FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban dalilin wannan zanga-zangar shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke gab da zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba su samu karfin gwiwa.
Kamfen din shugaban kasa Trump ya ce, tarurrukan da za a yi a mako mai zuwa guda biyar na neman karfafa masu aikin sa kai da kuma masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa ta majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya yi kasafin sunan sa, a cewar Reuters.
Taron da aka shirya a yau a Wembley, West Virginia, zai iya samun magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, a cewar Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ta wannan watan, wannan ne karo na biyu da Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morse, wanda ke kan jerin gwano.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morris cewa shugaban ya zo ne don ya yi kokarin inganta shi a zaben", in ji Simon Heder, wanda Reuters ta ruwaito cewa masanin siyasa ne a Jami'ar West Virginia.
