Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu na talla a Amurka, a kowace rana tana yabon fa'idodin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yada farfagandar ta hanyar kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba da ta gabata a kan wani shafi na jaridar China mai suna Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawa a jihar Iowa, inda ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin shiga zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters, cewa wannan wani sabon mataki ne na yakin neman zabe da Washington ke ci gaba da yi domin matsawa China.
