Tallafin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya ya yi niyya ne don a yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki hari daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ya goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na Amurka da na kasar Sin.
Jakadan Amurka a China Terry Branstead, tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce China ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa duka bulala.
Kamar yadda Branstead ya rubuta a cikin wani shafi na ranar Lahadi a cikin Des Moines Register, ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu ta kyauta, yanzu China tana maimaita wannan zalunci.
