Turai ta yi murna da lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 inda ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5-10.5 a Le Golf National da ke wajen birnin Paris.
Yanzu Amurka ta ci nasara sau shida a Turai kuma ba ta ci kofin Ryder Cup da aka yi a Turai ba a 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin bayan da babban dan kasar Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin kayar da Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Nicholson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya kusan duk gasar, ya jefa kwallon cikin ruwa bayan bugun uku, ya ci wasan a wasan 16 ga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari dan wasan Italiya ya yi fice a duk zagaye, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka yi nasara 5-0-0 tun 1979.
