An samu raguwar yawan masu shan magani a Pinellas, Manati da Sarasota
Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ta sanar da cewa akwai raguwar yawan ruwan sama a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar yarjejeniyar da'irar, an samu rahoton ci gaba da fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Ana samun furen Red wave mai nisan mil 130 (kilomita 208) daga Pinilas da ke arewa zuwa kudancin Li.
